            <title>China CloudFront SSL Plugin V2 - One-Stop Free SSL Certificate Management</title>
            <link>http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/</link>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/</guid>
            <description>&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/&#34; alt=&#34;Featured image of post China CloudFront SSL Plugin V2 - One-Stop Free SSL Certificate Management&#34; /&gt;&lt;p&gt;In today&amp;rsquo;s digital age, website security is paramount. In 2023, we released China CloudFront SSL Plugin for free SSL integration with CloudFront in China region. Now we&amp;rsquo;re pleased to announce V2.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;core-upgrades&#34;&gt;Core Upgrades&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;V2 introduces three core upgrades making certificate management simpler, safer, and more efficient.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-multi-project-management&#34;&gt;1. Multi-Project Management&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V1&lt;/strong&gt;: Each stack managed one project only&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V2&lt;/strong&gt;: Single stack manages multiple projects&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-graphical-interface&#34;&gt;2. Graphical Interface&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V1&lt;/strong&gt;: Manual API request construction via Swagger UI&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V2&lt;/strong&gt;: Intuitive GUI with button clicks&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-security-auth&#34;&gt;3. Security Auth&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V1&lt;/strong&gt;: No API security validation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V2&lt;/strong&gt;: Access Key authentication required&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;retained-features&#34;&gt;Retained Features&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;While bringing new features, we retained the most popular characteristics:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;✓ &lt;strong&gt;Cost&lt;/strong&gt; — Serverless, pay-per-use, auto-renewal every 30 days&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;✓ &lt;strong&gt;Automation&lt;/strong&gt; — Seamless CloudFront integration, auto certificate replacement, EventBridge scheduling&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;✓ &lt;strong&gt;Transparency&lt;/strong&gt; — Email notifications, graphical dashboard, multi-project monitoring&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;✓ &lt;strong&gt;Open Source&lt;/strong&gt; — All code open source, supports customization&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;architecture&#34;&gt;Architecture&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Built on serverless architecture with one-click CloudFormation deployment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Architecture&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;555px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;231&#34; height=&#34;731&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/architecture-v2.png&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/architecture-v2_hu_77ffabdb655b00f5.png 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/architecture-v2_hu_a1659a5a8d55333.png 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/architecture-v2.png 1691w&#34; width=&#34;1691&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Components&lt;/strong&gt;: Let&amp;rsquo;s Encrypt + Certbot + Lambda + API Gateway&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Storage&lt;/strong&gt;: DynamoDB (status) + S3 (backup) + IAM SSL (CloudFront association)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automation&lt;/strong&gt;: SNS (notifications) + EventBridge (scheduled renewal, default 30 days)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;deployment-demo&#34;&gt;Deployment Demo&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-stack&#34;&gt;Create Stack&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Deploy the main stack via CloudFormation template in 3-5 minutes with a stack name and Access Key.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Create Stack&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;426px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/new-stack.gif&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/new-stack_hu_801afb176afd33fd.gif 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/new-stack.gif 1280w&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-certificate-project&#34;&gt;Create Certificate Project&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create certificate projects in the GUI for domain sets. Supports multiple domains, configurable email and renewal intervals (30 days recommended). System auto-deploys sub-stacks.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Create Project&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;426px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/create-project.gif&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/create-project_hu_7162baf9cd7a6cb.gif 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/create-project.gif 1280w&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;attach-to-cloudfront&#34;&gt;Attach to CloudFront&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Certificates auto-upload to IAM SSL storage. Select in CloudFront console. Subsequent renewals replace seamlessly without manual intervention.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Attach SSL&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;426px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/attach-ssl.gif&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/attach-ssl_hu_635e22f67d718779.gif 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/attach-ssl.gif 1280w&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;update-project&#34;&gt;Update Project&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Update domain lists and intervals anytime; each change triggers re-issuance. Auto-handles certificate updates and cleanup.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Update Project&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;426px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/update-project.gif&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/update-project_hu_e4ce74cd9263387c.gif 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/update-project.gif 1280w&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;re-issue-certificate&#34;&gt;Re-issue Certificate&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Manual certificate update control for fault recovery, emergency updates, or testing. Re-executes the full certificate lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Re-issue&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;426px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/recert.gif&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/recert_hu_884274259bf0fe5a.gif 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2/images/recert.gif 1280w&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Deploy: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://console.amazonaws.cn/cloudformation/home?#/stacks/create/template?templateURL=https://aws-cn-getting-started.s3.cn-northwest-1.amazonaws.com.cn/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin_v2/ChinaCloudFrontSslPluginStackV2.template.json&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;One-click Deploy V2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Tutorial: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.amazonaws.cn/getting-started/tutorials/create-ssl-with-cloudfront/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;V2 Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;V2 delivers a more convenient certificate solution through multi-project architecture, graphical UI, and enhanced security.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;resources&#34;&gt;Resources&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.amazonaws.cn/getting-started/tutorials/create-ssl-with-cloudfront/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;V2 Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/sample-China-CloudFront-SSL-Plugin-V2&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub V2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/China-CloudFront-SSL-Plugin&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub V1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://docs.amazonaws.cn/aws/latest/userguide/cloudfront.html#feature-diff&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;CloudFront China Differences&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://docs.amazonaws.cn/IAM/latest/UserGuide/id_credentials_server-certs.html&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;IAM SSL Certificate Management&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://letsencrypt.org/docs/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s Encrypt Docs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://certbot.eff.org/pages/about&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Certbot Docs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;mailto:china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin@amazon.com&#34; &gt;Contact Us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;Original: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/cn/blogs/china/china-cloudfront-ssl-plugin-v2-a-one-stop-certificate-solution-for-cloudfront-in-china-region/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;AWS Blog&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/aws-samples/sample-China-CloudFront-SSL-Plugin-V2&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;</description>
